            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ENo%20greater%20work%20of%20the%20Lord%20is%20recorded%20in%20the%20Bible%20than%20David's%20slaying%20of%20Goliath.%20More%20than%20nine%20feet%20tall%2C%20Goliath%20presented%20the%20most%20imposing%20stature%20of%20any%20human%20being%20in%20history.%20The%20image%20of%20a%20little%20stripling%20boy%20walking%20and%20then%20running%20toward%20such%20a%20giant%20stirs%20the%20courage%20of%20all%20who%20read%20the%20tale.%20Let's%20note%20three%20of%20this%20story's%20many%20lessons.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20first%20lesson%20deals%20with%20the%20boldness%20of%20a%20person%20who%20is%20anointed%20by%20God.%20Saul%20and%20all%20his%20men%20were%20scared%20to%20death%20of%20Goliath%2C%20but%20the%20young%20man%20who%20had%20been%20anointed%20by%20God%20had%20no%20sense%20of%20fear.%20He%20had%20no%20concern%20or%20worry%20because%20his%20trust%20was%20in%20the%20God%20who%20had%20always%20helped%20him.%20He%20boldly%20proclaimed%2C%20%22The%20Lord%20who%20saved%20me%20from%20the%20claws%20of%20the%20lion%20and%20the%20bear%20will%20save%20me%20from%20this%20Philistine!%22%20(1%20Samuel%2017%3A37).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20second%20lesson%20concerns%20the%20methods%20of%20God.%20David%20refused%20Saul's%20bulky%20armor%2C%20saying%20only%20that%20he%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20without%20it.%20He%20was%20choosing%20God's%20methods%20over%20the%20methods%20of%20the%20world.%20Trust%20in%20the%20things%20of%20this%20world%20rather%20than%20the%20things%20of%20God%20will%20never%20bring%20success%20when%20facing%20an%20overwhelming%20battle.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20third%20lesson%20illustrates%20the%20works%20of%20the%20Lord.%20God%20can%20take%20the%20smallest%20human%20weapons%20and%20warriors%20and%20demolish%20the%20mightiest%20foes.%20Who%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20five%20stones%20in%20the%20hand%20of%20a%20boy%20could%20bring%20down%20the%20mighty%20Goliath%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPsalm%20111%3A2%20reminds%20us%2C%20%22How%20amazing%20are%20the%20deeds%20of%20the%20Lord!%20All%20who%20delight%20in%20him%20should%20ponder%20them.%22%20Run%20boldly%20toward%20your%20%22Goliath.%22%20He%20must%20come%20down%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Lord!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
