            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Samuel%2017%3A1-18%3A4%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EGoliath%20Challenges%20the%20Israelites%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Philistines%20now%20mustered%20their%20army%20for%20battle%20and%20camped%20between%20Socoh%20in%20Judah%20and%20Azekah%20at%20Ephes-dammim.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESaul%20countered%20by%20gathering%20his%20Israelite%20troops%20near%20the%20valley%20of%20Elah.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20Philistines%20and%20Israelites%20faced%20each%20other%20on%20opposite%20hills%2C%20with%20the%20valley%20between%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Goliath%2C%20a%20Philistine%20champion%20from%20Gath%2C%20came%20out%20of%20the%20Philistine%20ranks%20to%20face%20the%20forces%20of%20Israel.%20He%20was%20over%20nine%20feet%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E17%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E6%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%20and%201%26%23xA0%3Bspan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bwhich%20totals%20about%209.75%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%20or%203%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D%3B%20Dead%20Sea%20Scrolls%20and%20Greek%20version%20read%20%3Cem%3E4%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%20and%201%26%23xA0%3Bspan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bwhich%20totals%20about%206.75%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%20or%202%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20tall!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20wore%20a%20bronze%20helmet%2C%20and%20his%20bronze%20coat%20of%20mail%20weighed%20125%26%23xA0%3Bpounds.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E17%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E5%2C000%20shekels%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B57%26%23xA0%3Bkilograms%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20also%20wore%20bronze%20leg%20armor%2C%20and%20he%20carried%20a%20bronze%20javelin%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20shaft%20of%20his%20spear%20was%20as%20heavy%20and%20thick%20as%20a%20weaver%26%23x2019%3Bs%20beam%2C%20tipped%20with%20an%20iron%20spearhead%20that%20weighed%2015%26%23xA0%3Bpounds.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E17%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E600%26%23xA0%3Bshekels%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B6.8%26%23xA0%3Bkilograms%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20His%20armor%20bearer%20walked%20ahead%20of%20him%20carrying%20a%20shield.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EGoliath%20stood%20and%20shouted%20a%20taunt%20across%20to%20the%20Israelites.%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20are%20you%20all%20coming%20out%20to%20fight%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20called.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20the%20Philistine%20champion%2C%20but%20you%20are%20only%20the%20servants%20of%20Saul.%20Choose%20one%20man%20to%20come%20down%20here%20and%20fight%20me!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20he%20kills%20me%2C%20then%20we%20will%20be%20your%20slaves.%20But%20if%20I%20kill%20him%2C%20you%20will%20be%20our%20slaves!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20defy%20the%20armies%20of%20Israel%20today!%20Send%20me%20a%20man%20who%20will%20fight%20me!%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Saul%20and%20the%20Israelites%20heard%20this%2C%20they%20were%20terrified%20and%20deeply%20shaken.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_12%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJesse%20Sends%20David%20to%20Saul%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Camp%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20David%20was%20the%20son%20of%20a%20man%20named%20Jesse%2C%20an%20Ephrathite%20from%20Bethlehem%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Judah.%20Jesse%20was%20an%20old%20man%20at%20that%20time%2C%20and%20he%20had%20eight%20sons.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_17_13%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2217%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EJesse%26%23x2019%3Bs%20three%20oldest%20sons%26%23x2014%3BEliab%2C%20Abinadab%2C%20and%20Shimea%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E17%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EShammah%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Shimea%3B%20compare%201%26%23xA0%3BChr%202%3A13%3B%